\begin_inset Formula $\omega/\omega_{p,z}$
\end_inset

 in modo che il polo o lo zero si trovino sempre in 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega/\omega_{p,z}=1$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left|G_{p,z}\left(j\frac{\omega}{\omega_{p,z}}\right)\right|_{{\scriptscriptstyle dB}}=\mp20\log_{10}\sqrt{1-\left(\frac{\omega}{\omega_{p,z}}\right)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


