\begin_inset Formula 
\[
P_{i}e^{-p_{i}t}+P_{i}^{*}e^{-p_{i}^{*}t}
\]

\end_inset

Se esprimiamo i poli 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{i}=\sigma_{i}+j\omega_{i}$
\end_inset

 e i residui 
